item.title: Existential Crisis
item.description: Periodically throughout my life, I asked myself the same questions as Snoopy. It was during one of those periods, a high school teacher of mine told me the answer was in The Hitch Hiker’s Guide to the Galaxy had an answer to the riddle: What is the answer to life, the universe, and everything? So, naturally, I got the book, and skipped to the section that had the answer…
